  "text": "Finally, we note that MLSL has already been applied into the global constrained black-box optimization setting in [CITATION_1] . The proposed method, MLSL-MADS, integrates MLSL with a mesh adaptive direct search (MADS) method [CITATION_2] to find multiple local minima of an inverse transport problem involving black-box functions.",
